  <title>Environment</title>
  <para>
   This document applies to the following products and product versions:
  </para>
  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     &sles;&nbsp;15&nbsp;SP3, 15&nbsp;SP2, 15&nbsp;SP1, 15&nbsp;GA,
